PROPOSITION 103 (STATE INSURANCE COMMISSIONER); GOVERNMENT REGULATION; COMMON 
CAUSE; LETTERS; ZELMAN, WALTER; GILLESPIE, ROXANI M; MISMANAGEMENT; CALIFORNIA 
-- GOVERNMENT 
</P>
