COUPLE SING ELIAS' PRAISES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
My wife and I attended Diane Elias' recital at St. Andrew's Presbyterian 
Church, and we were disappointed with Bruce Burroughs' review ("Mezzo Diane 
Elias in Hometown Newport Recital," Calendar, Aug. 8). 
</P>
<P>
We thoroughly enjoyed the choice of songs and the singing as well as the 
opportunity to hear Miss Elias sing. 
</P>
<P>
We do not agree with Mr. Burroughs' review. 
</P>
<P>
Mr. and Mrs. ROBERT D. HUNTER, Huntington Beach 
